Sentencas: A series of La0.7Sr0.3Mn3-delta (LSM)-based perovskite cathode material with B-site Mg-doped composition La0.7Sr0.3Mn1-xMgxO3-delta (LSMM, x = 0, 0.1, 0.2) was successfully synthesized by a combined EDTA-citrate complexing method.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of B-site Mg-doped La0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ perovskite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The effect of the introduction of Mg into the Mn-site of La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 on the structural characteristics and electrochemical properties of the samples was specifically investigated.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of B-site Mg-doped La0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ perovskite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Among all the samples, La0.7Sr0.3MnO3Mg0.2O3-delta (LSMM20) showed larger BET surface areas (8.72 m(2)/g), a lower thermal expansion coefficient of -10.6 x 10(-6) K-1 in a temperature range of 50-900 degrees C and a higher oxygen vacancy concentration.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of B-site Mg-doped La0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ perovskite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The good electrochemical performance of LSMM20 was manifested from its lower polarization resistance (Rp), resulting in a maximum power density of 187 mW cm-2 for an electrolyte supported single cell at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of B-site Mg-doped La0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ perovskite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This study indicates the potential of LSMM20 as a cathode candidate material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Structural and electrochemical properties of B-site Mg-doped La0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ perovskite cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
